499
00:35:38,091 --> 00:35:40,559
I don't understand kids.

500
00:35:40,771 --> 00:35:43,127
When I was her age, I never
would've taken a foot.

501
00:35:43,332 --> 00:35:46,688
David, I can help. I'm a cop.
That's what I do for a living.

502
00:35:48,052 --> 00:35:50,613
You find feet?

503
