What the fuck am I gonna do?

504
00:35:53,013 --> 00:35:54,605
Tell me who lived here again.

505
00:35:55,774 --> 00:35:58,493
The Fritzens.

506
00:35:59,414 --> 00:36:02,168
I have totally fucked things up.
