528
00:37:54,793 --> 00:37:58,946
- You can't control things. Nobody can.
- Shut up.

529
00:37:59,154 --> 00:38:01,543
There's only one thing that's certain.

530
00:38:02,275 --> 00:38:08,112
- Everything changes.
- Shut. Up.

531
00:38:29,759 --> 00:38:31,033
