- Man...

534
00:38:36,600 --> 00:38:39,274
A witness already said she saw you
running down the hall...

535
00:38:39,481 --> 00:38:42,518
...screaming the crazy funeral-home
girl put a foot in your locker.

536
00:38:42,801 --> 00:38:44,440
It was a joke. It was just a joke.

537
00:38:44,642 --> 00:38:47,156
She's kind of a loser,
and we all pick on her.

538
00:38:47,362 --> 00:38:51,117
- She totally asks for it.
- Modern technology is really something.

539
00:38:52,443 --> 00:38:55,116
- I don't care, man.
- You should.

540
00:38:55,323 --> 00:38:58,873
